nodes.text: In 138 ABY, an officer was stationed aboard the Star Destroyer Animus.

After the ship, responding to a distress call from AG-37's freighter with Ania Solo aboard, picked up the freighter, the officer greeted Solo and informed her that Empress Marasiah Fel was impressed with Solo's actions regarding saving the Imperial Knight Yalta Val from the Carreras system, and wished for Solo to speak to her and the other members of the Galactic Federation Triumvirate in a formal audience.
